{"tid":1028757,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Zuji 冇退嘅費用，銀行成功追返了","createTime":"2019-02-19T17:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T14:34:05.000Z","uid":38376,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"203acb9cbf162a96fbdcadbe474b350595011205","tid":1028757,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"上年10月底在Zuji 訂左package，點知hotel firm左機票又firm唔到，一直hold住，後來跟跟吓Zuji down左，結果就係機票要重新買過，然後自己打去問酒店個booking係點，酒店開頭都話firm，後來佢搵我地話怕Zuji未必找到數比佢，所以cancel左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果d錢就凍過水嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩根據Visa 同 Master規則，執笠嘅公司提供唔到服務的話，銀行需要協助退款，所以我地打比銀行，填左張Dispute form，聲明個間公司Service not rendered，嗰間公司就需要進行回應，Zuji 回應唔到提供左服務嘅憑據，所以，兩個月後，D錢就chargeback成功，退左款返信用卡度喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e698767510e9412d15299f7a11531737bf993e9c","tid":1028757,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:51:22.000Z","msg":"恭喜sam巴"},{"pid":"219127c55f11714dd1cbf3a16356a23a74603834","tid":1028757,"uid":19421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"大陸野真係信唔撚得過<br />\nCtrip都係垃鳩圾"}]}